title: Spotted: Man United star appears in training after injury ahead of Saint-Etienne clash
text:
1 of 17 Man United have received an injury boost ahead of their Europa League clash 
The 31-year-old has been struggling with a tooth problem and reportedly underwent a root canal at the weekend, but has raised eyebrows by appearing in training with the rest of the United squad . 
Manager Jose Mourinho had previously ruled Rooney out of featuring against Saint-Etienne on Wednesday, while the Red Devils' record goalscorer is also a doubt for the EFL Cup final against Southampton.
